Seoul Toy Museum is located on Zhendong Road. It is said that the word TOYKINO is a combination of toy "TOY" and German cinema "KINO". The toys are simply the favorites of children and big friends. It is worth coming! ! ! The small shop at the door is so good to visit ～

The Toy Museum is not a huge display, but it's also interesting, with nine sets of old toys and Barbies of all ages. Then the Star Wars toys brought back memories. Those who like to collect dolls can go to the Transformers and Saints series.

Toy Museum is a very interesting place, three stories high, there are many rooms to explore, dozens of display cabinets filled with toys, the room has a low ceiling, so if you are tall, pay attention to your head, there is an old-fashioned toy shop on the first floor, selling chessboard games and cloth bag puppets.

Seoul Toy Museum, Korea (TOYKINO MUSEUM), the most trendy toy museum. The largest model and toy museum in Korea is also an industry model of modern toy museums. As the name implies, TOYKINO is a combination of English toy "TOY" and German cinema "KINO", where you can watch a variety of toys, role models and so on in various countries around the world.

Toy Museum is the largest model toy museum in China. It has more than 400,000 models and exhibits many themes according to different seasons. Character models with super popular movie heroes and symbolic actions reproduce the famous scenes in the movie classically.
I don't know if this is the largest toy museum in Korea. There are too many images we see in cartoons. It's so funny that I don't want to go. It reminds us of many childhood memories.
